<br>
All of the others are FFA zones, and you can lead raids to them whenever you wish.  <br>
<br>
PoG is a particularly good spot, assuming that you can get enough &quot;darkies&quot; together to go up there.  Drops are in line with Kael armor drops, but without the annoying gems to find.  Unless Tunare is up it is usually pretty vacant there.<br>
<br>
PoM I have not done much research on.  It is also, from my understanding, virtually always vacant.  I don't know how hard it is, and what the drops are here.<br>
<br>
PoP planes are also something else to look into.  You probably know as much as me about these.<br>
<br>
Feel free to investigate these and lead raids to them if you wish.  Unfortunately as I am involved in an alliance now and leading many of the raids for that alliance I do not have time to plan and lead any raids other than the rotational planes raids.  The best way to get something done is to do it yourself, if you truly want to do something.  I am sure that there will be many sharing your thoughts that would be willing to come and help in any way necessary. <p>Farrnusno <BR>
